cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for semi-supervised learning for text classification using neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of state-of-the-art SSL algorithms such as $\Pi$-model, temporal ensembling, mean teacher, etc., which are related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of dropout, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE).
